query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('c++17',
'guava',
'gulp',
'html5-video',
'mingw',
'onclick',
'singleton',
'sublimetext3',
'subprocess',
'testng',
'themes',
'timestamp',
'typo3',
'x86-64',
'xss');
